    <intervention_type>Other</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Relaxation CD</intervention_name>
    <description>A music CD specifically created for this study to promote effective sleep while deployed. It includes sleep instructions tailored to the military deployment environment. The CD includes a voice directed meditation component that helps focus the listener on relaxation in preparation for sleep. The second track is specifically designed music to promote slow breathing and induce sleep.</description>
    <arm_group_label>1</arm_group_label>
